title: Identification and characterization of wHeat long non-protein coding RNAs responsive to powdery mildew infection and Heat stress by using microarray analysis and SBS sequencing.
description_of_lnc: The Heat responsive long npcRNA TahlnRNA27 contained Ta-miR2010 family sequences, and was up-regulated in 'TAM107' (Heat tolerant cultivar) 1 h after Heat treatment
